# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different platforms or sub-versions:
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Using Poetry, it's recommended to include poetry.lock in version control.
#poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Using PDM, it's recommended to include pdm.lock in version control.
